<p>execute => 验证用户身份，失败返回INPUT</p>

<p>*return: *</p>

<p>"student" => student/StuInfo.action</p>

<p>"teacher" => teacher/TeacherInfo.action</p>

<p>"admin" => admin/AdminInfo.action</p>

<p>ERROR/INPUT => /pages/Login.jsp(with validation error)</p>

